> **A modern, performant, and responsive portfolio** showcasing my skills, projects, and journey as a Front-End Developer. Built with cutting-edge technologies for optimal user experience.

🌐 **Live Demo**: [portfolio-alpha-beige-530yawe3ff.vercel.app](https://portfolio-alpha-beige-530yawe3ff.vercel.app/)

---

## ✨ Features

- 🎨 **Modern UI/UX** with smooth animations and responsive design
- ⚡ **Blazing fast performance** (100 Lighthouse score)
- 📱 **Mobile-first approach** with perfect responsiveness
- 🌓 **Dark/Light mode** support
- 📊 **Interactive elements** to engage visitors
- 📝 **Dynamic content** easy to update

---

## 🏗️ Project Structure

```bash
src/
├── app/                # Next.js 13+ App Router
│   ├── layout.tsx      # Root layout with metadata
│   └── page.tsx        # Homepage composition
│
├── components/         # Reusable UI components
│   ├── common/         # Shared components (Buttons, Cards...)
│   ├── sections/       # Page sections (Hero, Skills...)
│   └── ui/            # Custom UI elements
│
├── lib/                # Utilities and helpers
├── constants/          # Data and configuration
├── styles/             # Global styles and themes
├── public/             # Static assets
└── types/              # TypeScript type definitions
